1
00:01:31,720 --> 00:01:35,009
[Wind Direction]

2
00:01:35,440 --> 00:01:37,940
[Episode 14]

3
00:01:38,979 --> 00:01:42,660
[Winter of 1994]

4
00:01:55,780 --> 00:01:59,140
We could just sleep together gently.

5
00:01:59,870 --> 00:02:00,590
We're here?

6
00:02:07,830 --> 00:02:09,289
We've arrived at my place.

7
00:02:10,130 --> 00:02:10,910
Xiu.

8
00:02:12,040 --> 00:02:13,520
I really love you.

9
00:02:13,550 --> 00:02:14,750
You know that, right?

10
00:02:17,460 --> 00:02:18,470
Who is it?

11
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:21,090
My daughter.

12
00:02:22,420 --> 00:02:24,020
She's older than I expected.

13
00:02:24,079 --> 00:02:25,200
So what?

14
00:02:26,100 --> 00:02:27,760
She's useless, just a burden.

15
00:02:28,750 --> 00:02:30,010
Why are the lights off?

16
00:02:31,900 --> 00:02:32,740
Turn them on!

17
00:02:36,710 --> 00:02:37,390
Please.

18
00:02:37,950 --> 00:02:39,310
Thank you.

19
00:02:39,579 --> 00:02:40,700
You're welcome.

20
00:02:43,150 --> 00:02:44,350
What?

21
00:02:44,610 --> 00:02:46,240
The sofa's sagging!

22
00:02:46,610 --> 00:02:48,630
You broke our sofa.

23
00:02:48,660 --> 00:02:49,390
You have to pay for it.

24
00:02:49,390 --> 00:02:50,079
How?

25
00:02:50,610 --> 00:02:52,110
How should I pay?

26
00:02:52,110 --> 00:02:53,470
You tell me.

27
00:02:53,470 --> 00:02:54,710
You tell me.

28
00:02:54,730 --> 00:02:55,680
I'm thirsty.

29
00:02:57,890 --> 00:02:58,890
Get us some water.

30
00:03:03,350 --> 00:03:05,470
My sofa is expensive.

31
00:03:08,310 --> 00:03:09,430
I want a drink.

32
00:03:09,930 --> 00:03:10,790
Do you have any?

33
00:03:14,460 --> 00:03:15,390
Call her "Aunt."

34
00:03:21,670 --> 00:03:22,829
Are you mute?

35
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:24,010
No need!

36
00:03:24,030 --> 00:03:25,070
No need!

37
00:03:25,100 --> 00:03:26,030
No need!

38
00:03:27,370 --> 00:03:29,450
Are you drunk and acting crazy?

39
00:03:29,950 --> 00:03:30,829
You're scaring me!

40
00:03:30,829 --> 00:03:31,420
I'm leaving!

41
00:03:31,420 --> 00:03:32,870
Don't go, please.

42
00:03:34,220 --> 00:03:35,150
Don't be afraid.

43
00:03:35,750 --> 00:03:37,210
Get back to your homework.

44
00:03:38,290 --> 00:03:39,860
You're nuts.

45
00:03:52,310 --> 00:03:53,079
What's this?

46
00:03:53,980 --> 00:03:54,780
Chicken soup.

47
00:04:00,320 --> 00:04:01,650
Why does it smell so bad?

48
00:04:03,200 --> 00:04:04,660
Your dad still isn't back?

49
00:04:09,270 --> 00:04:11,730
It's been three days since the baby was born.

50
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,640
Where did he go?

51
00:04:20,269 --> 00:04:20,990
Check the drawer—

52
00:04:20,990 --> 00:04:22,720
see if the money is still there.

53
00:04:34,670 --> 00:04:35,300
Is it?

54
00:04:37,150 --> 00:04:37,880
Gone.

55
00:04:50,510 --> 00:04:51,670
Page 224.

56
00:04:53,110 --> 00:04:54,190
Tell him someone in the family died,

57
00:04:54,190 --> 00:04:56,320
and he needs to come home immediately.

58
00:04:56,430 --> 00:04:57,150
Yes.

59
00:04:58,190 --> 00:04:59,320
The last name is Lin.

60
00:04:59,430 --> 00:05:00,800
Call him 50 times!

61
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:08,760
Can you stop crying?

62
00:05:08,790 --> 00:05:10,110
Cry, cry, cry!

63
00:05:10,110 --> 00:05:11,710
Is that all you know how to do?

64
00:05:12,370 --> 00:05:13,570
Enough! Stop crying.

65
00:05:14,510 --> 00:05:15,150
Don't cry.

66
00:05:17,650 --> 00:05:18,570
It's okay.

67
00:05:20,670 --> 00:05:21,710
I wouldn't be in this situation

68
00:05:21,710 --> 00:05:23,310
if it weren't for you.

69
00:05:25,070 --> 00:05:26,000
Don't cry.

70
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:27,640
Don't cry.

71
00:05:27,670 --> 00:05:28,400
I'm so tired.

72
00:05:50,590 --> 00:05:51,600
I'm sorry.

73
00:05:51,620 --> 00:05:52,940
Zi, don't cry.

74
00:05:52,970 --> 00:05:53,840
Don't cry.

75
00:05:59,550 --> 00:06:00,790
I'm sorry.

76
00:06:02,070 --> 00:06:04,450
[The Seabird]

77
00:06:05,350 --> 00:06:06,550
Zi had a fever

78
00:06:06,930 --> 00:06:08,560
for three whole days,

79
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:10,840
almost didn't make it.

80
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:16,860
Lin Xiu went to look for Yuan Yong,

81
00:06:17,150 --> 00:06:18,270
and they didn't come back

82
00:06:18,270 --> 00:06:19,200
for half a month.

83
00:06:19,790 --> 00:06:20,670
Yuan Yong somehow

84
00:06:20,670 --> 00:06:21,650
got a car,

85
00:06:22,550 --> 00:06:24,030
and they started scamming people

86
00:06:24,030 --> 00:06:25,150
for money.

87
00:06:25,670 --> 00:06:26,550
They never

88
00:06:26,550 --> 00:06:27,410
cared about Zi.

89
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,670
In fact, because she was a girl,

90
00:06:29,670 --> 00:06:31,270
they even wanted to sell her.

91
00:06:33,670 --> 00:06:36,000
Back then, I was too afraid to go to school.

92
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:38,310
I just held onto Zi and hid.

93
00:06:39,330 --> 00:06:41,530
Later, when Yuan Yong got into trouble,

94
00:06:42,110 --> 00:06:43,620
we lost our house.

95
00:06:44,470 --> 00:06:45,870
I sat with Zi

96
00:06:46,550 --> 00:06:47,790
outside the office building

97
00:06:47,790 --> 00:06:48,640
for three days

98
00:06:50,790 --> 00:06:51,680
until a manager came out

99
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:52,390
and gave us

100
00:06:52,390 --> 00:06:53,850
our current place to stay.

101
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:55,890
That's how we survived.

102
00:06:57,810 --> 00:06:59,090
Sometimes I think,

103
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:02,240
it's a good thing Yuan Yong and Lin Xiu

104
00:07:02,780 --> 00:07:04,240
ran into trouble and left.

105
00:07:05,510 --> 00:07:06,830
Otherwise, Zi and I

106
00:07:07,930 --> 00:07:09,330
wouldn't have made it.

107
00:07:11,270 --> 00:07:12,230
Mom.

108
00:07:12,390 --> 00:07:13,910
Zi seems a bit tired.

109
00:07:13,910 --> 00:07:15,580
I'll take her inside to sleep for a bit.

110
00:07:15,580 --> 00:07:16,640
Go ahead, go ahead.

111
00:07:21,700 --> 00:07:23,260
So, do you know

112
00:07:23,280 --> 00:07:24,940
where your dad kept the money?

113
00:07:25,790 --> 00:07:26,390
Don't...

114
00:07:26,630 --> 00:07:28,610
Why bring that up?

115
00:07:29,440 --> 00:07:30,590
I just want to get a sense of things.

116
00:07:30,590 --> 00:07:33,390
That way, I can tell the police when the time comes.

117
00:07:34,590 --> 00:07:35,310
Yuan Yong

118
00:07:35,310 --> 00:07:36,560
hid a metal box at home

119
00:07:36,580 --> 00:07:37,780
with some money in it.

120
00:07:38,750 --> 00:07:41,080
He didn't have time to take it when he left.

121
00:07:42,790 --> 00:07:44,270
But I already told the police,

122
00:07:44,270 --> 00:07:45,510
and I handed over the money—

123
00:07:45,510 --> 00:07:46,510
over 10,000 yuan.

124
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:49,820
He scammed tens of thousands, though.

125
00:07:51,270 --> 00:07:53,600
I don't know where the rest of the money is.

126
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,750
He hasn't come back to look for me since.

127
00:07:55,750 --> 00:07:56,590
He wouldn't dare.

128
00:07:56,590 --> 00:07:58,720
He'd be arrested as soon as he showed up.

129
00:07:58,720 --> 00:07:59,430
People like that

130
00:07:59,430 --> 00:08:00,680
are infuriating.

131
00:08:00,710 --> 00:08:01,570
They don't just

132
00:08:01,760 --> 00:08:03,260
both of them are bad.

133
00:08:03,980 --> 00:08:05,450
They even

134
00:08:05,520 --> 00:08:06,910
ruin their own children.

135
00:08:06,910 --> 00:08:07,570
They should

136
00:08:07,790 --> 00:08:09,150
be shot.

137
00:08:09,170 --> 00:08:11,070
Why are you saying this

138
00:08:11,070 --> 00:08:13,070
in front of the kids?

139
00:08:14,030 --> 00:08:15,030
She's old enough

140
00:08:15,030 --> 00:08:15,500
to know exactly

141
00:08:15,500 --> 00:08:17,300
what kind of person Yuan Yong is.

142
00:08:22,210 --> 00:08:22,850
Mom,

143
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:24,270
she really loves that...

144
00:08:24,270 --> 00:08:25,270
Keep an eye on her.

145
00:08:25,630 --> 00:08:26,710
She's asleep.

146
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:28,050
She's asleep?

147
00:08:34,110 --> 00:08:34,789
Well...

148
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:37,750
Since Zi's fever last time,

149
00:08:37,789 --> 00:08:39,049
has anything changed?

150
00:08:40,159 --> 00:08:42,309
She seems to sleep more now

151
00:08:43,070 --> 00:08:44,720
and doesn't cry as much.

152
00:08:45,070 --> 00:08:47,130
I even think she's grown more mature.

153
00:08:49,770 --> 00:08:50,730
Uncle Cheng,

154
00:08:51,190 --> 00:08:52,030
is it because of

155
00:08:52,030 --> 00:08:52,830
that fever

156
00:08:52,850 --> 00:08:54,420
that her hearing got damaged?

157
00:08:54,420 --> 00:08:56,480
She used to respond when I called her.

158
00:08:57,850 --> 00:08:59,090
It's possible.

159
00:09:00,390 --> 00:09:01,430
It's all my fault.

160
00:09:02,310 --> 00:09:03,750
If only I had come back

161
00:09:03,750 --> 00:09:04,350
earlier that day.

162
00:09:04,350 --> 00:09:04,950
No, no.

163
00:09:04,950 --> 00:09:05,790
Maybe if she hadn't been caught in the rain,

164
00:09:05,790 --> 00:09:07,650
things would've been different.

165
00:09:07,980 --> 00:09:10,070
Shanqing, calm down.

166
00:09:10,290 --> 00:09:11,200
How about this?

167
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,350
I'll arrange

168
00:09:12,350 --> 00:09:14,210
a more thorough check-up for her.

169
00:09:16,380 --> 00:09:16,900
Dad.

170
00:09:21,300 --> 00:09:22,230
Can she be cured?

171
00:09:22,800 --> 00:09:23,600
Treatment takes time;

172
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:25,290
it's not something that happens overnight.

173
00:09:25,290 --> 00:09:26,770
We need to be patient,

174
00:09:26,800 --> 00:09:27,770
with gradual tests

175
00:09:27,770 --> 00:09:28,900
and treatment.

176
00:09:29,670 --> 00:09:30,320
Yes.

177
00:09:30,640 --> 00:09:32,000
Shanqing, don't worry.

178
00:09:32,070 --> 00:09:32,990
My dad is the best

179
00:09:32,990 --> 00:09:34,690
ENT specialist here.

180
00:09:34,870 --> 00:09:35,710
He even cured

181
00:09:35,710 --> 00:09:36,630
the factory manager's hearing.

182
00:09:36,630 --> 00:09:38,030
Zi will be fine for sure.

183
00:09:38,230 --> 00:09:39,360
Yeah, he even helped

184
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:40,660
an 80-year-old lady

185
00:09:40,690 --> 00:09:41,560
hear again.

186
00:09:41,820 --> 00:09:43,350
Zi will definitely be fine,

187
00:09:43,370 --> 00:09:43,850
right?

188
00:09:44,190 --> 00:09:45,390
Don't worry about it.

189
00:09:46,830 --> 00:09:48,090
People say it's karma,

190
00:09:49,870 --> 00:09:51,230
but it's clearly their fault.

191
00:09:51,230 --> 00:09:53,010
Why does Zi have to suffer?

192
00:09:53,900 --> 00:09:55,740
She didn't do anything wrong.

193
00:09:57,270 --> 00:09:58,190
Why is life

194
00:09:58,190 --> 00:09:59,380
so unfair?

195
00:10:00,030 --> 00:10:02,220
Shanqing, life is like this.

196
00:10:02,570 --> 00:10:04,290
Sometimes it's smooth,

197
00:10:04,790 --> 00:10:06,790
and sometimes we hit rough patches.

198
00:10:06,970 --> 00:10:08,830
But when we're in the tough times,

199
00:10:09,220 --> 00:10:10,610
we can't give up.

200
00:10:11,790 --> 00:10:13,650
Once this difficult time passes,

201
00:10:13,660 --> 00:10:14,990
things will get better.

202
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:18,450
They'll definitely

203
00:10:18,600 --> 00:10:20,450
be caught by the police.

204
00:10:23,190 --> 00:10:24,530
Zi will recover.

205
00:10:25,110 --> 00:10:27,510
Everything will turn out fine for you both.

206
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:35,520
Everything will be fine.

207
00:10:44,830 --> 00:10:46,230
Back then, when Yuan Yong

208
00:10:46,480 --> 00:10:47,320
got drunk,

209
00:10:47,980 --> 00:10:49,780
he would come home and hit my mom.

210
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:52,060
My mom always said,

211
00:10:52,540 --> 00:10:54,620
"Family shame shouldn't be exposed."

212
00:10:54,620 --> 00:10:56,550
She was afraid of the humiliation,

213
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:59,510
afraid that others would look down on us,

214
00:10:59,510 --> 00:11:00,510
so she endured it.

215
00:11:04,340 --> 00:11:05,800
I was too young at the time,

216
00:11:06,920 --> 00:11:08,980
and there wasn't anything I could do.

217
00:11:12,050 --> 00:11:13,710
The saddest part is that my mom

218
00:11:15,380 --> 00:11:16,990
never had a single good day.

219
00:11:22,170 --> 00:11:23,500
It's all in the past now.

220
00:11:28,340 --> 00:11:29,470
Do you know

221
00:11:29,470 --> 00:11:30,930
what my biggest regret is?

222
00:11:31,070 --> 00:11:31,670
What?

223
00:11:33,580 --> 00:11:34,950
I don't even know

224
00:11:35,760 --> 00:11:37,020
where my mom is buried.

225
00:11:39,370 --> 00:11:42,230
Every time I mentioned her, Yuan Yong would beat me.

226
00:11:49,510 --> 00:11:51,910
This is the first time I've ever talked about it.

227
00:11:51,910 --> 00:11:53,030
Did I scare you?

228
00:11:56,590 --> 00:11:57,230
No,

229
00:12:00,150 --> 00:12:01,150
I just don't know

230
00:12:01,150 --> 00:12:02,340
how to comfort you.

231
00:12:04,160 --> 00:12:05,560
What's there to comfort?

232
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:07,370
It's all in the past.

233
00:12:09,860 --> 00:12:11,120
What's most important

234
00:12:12,380 --> 00:12:13,660
to me now is Zi.

235
00:12:15,750 --> 00:12:17,230
No matter what the cost,

236
00:12:18,630 --> 00:12:20,760
I'm going to make sure she gets better.

237
00:12:22,020 --> 00:12:22,820
Zi,

238
00:12:23,510 --> 00:12:24,510
let's go home.

239
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:25,840
Let's go.

240
00:12:32,240 --> 00:12:33,360
I'm really fine.

241
00:12:33,390 --> 00:12:34,070
Take it slow, Mom.

242
00:12:34,070 --> 00:12:34,950
Slow down, slow down.

243
00:12:34,950 --> 00:12:35,750
Why didn't you

244
00:12:35,750 --> 00:12:37,230
turn off the lights?

245
00:12:37,550 --> 00:12:39,230
They've been on for so long—

246
00:12:39,230 --> 00:12:40,310
-what a waste of electricity.
-I forgot.

247
00:12:40,310 --> 00:12:41,640
-Why didn't you...
-I forgot.

248
00:12:41,640 --> 00:12:43,280
Min, change your shoes.

249
00:12:43,310 --> 00:12:44,570
-Change shoes.
-Okay.

250
00:12:44,760 --> 00:12:45,840
The lights

251
00:12:46,110 --> 00:12:47,870
have been on for days.

252
00:12:48,150 --> 00:12:50,500
Think about how much that costs.

253
00:12:51,820 --> 00:12:52,710
While I'm not home,

254
00:12:52,710 --> 00:12:53,750
you've turned the house

255
00:12:53,750 --> 00:12:55,150
into a mess.

256
00:12:56,560 --> 00:12:58,910
How long has this food been left out?

257
00:12:58,910 --> 00:12:59,350
And why isn't anything

258
00:12:59,350 --> 00:13:00,550
cleaned up after meals?

259
00:13:00,550 --> 00:13:01,480
Let me handle it.

260
00:13:01,480 --> 00:13:02,580
Why didn't you clean it up?

261
00:13:02,580 --> 00:13:03,470
Give it to me.

262
00:13:03,470 --> 00:13:04,430
Can you take a rest?

263
00:13:04,430 --> 00:13:05,550
You just got discharged.

264
00:13:05,550 --> 00:13:07,150
Look at the house!

265
00:13:07,150 --> 00:13:08,190
Dirty socks

266
00:13:08,190 --> 00:13:09,430
thrown everywhere.

267
00:13:09,450 --> 00:13:11,220
-Mom. Mom.
-Can you just

268
00:13:11,250 --> 00:13:12,270
-put away...
-Mom.

269
00:13:12,270 --> 00:13:13,070
Let me do it.

270
00:13:13,070 --> 00:13:13,830
-Let me.
-Can't you…

271
00:13:13,830 --> 00:13:14,720
-These things...
-Give them to me.

272
00:13:14,720 --> 00:13:15,430
Help your mom

273
00:13:15,430 --> 00:13:16,670
sit down.

274
00:13:16,670 --> 00:13:17,270
-Give them to me.
-Just put the socks

275
00:13:17,270 --> 00:13:18,150
and dirty clothes

276
00:13:18,150 --> 00:13:19,190
in the washing machine.

277
00:13:19,190 --> 00:13:20,040
Mom, sit down.

278
00:13:20,190 --> 00:13:20,830
There's more.

279
00:13:20,830 --> 00:13:21,870
There's another one.

280
00:13:21,870 --> 00:13:22,830
Socks over there too!

281
00:13:22,830 --> 00:13:24,430
-Let me handle it.
-Hurry up.

282
00:13:32,670 --> 00:13:34,530
What happened to your foot, Li Si?

283
00:13:35,060 --> 00:13:35,630
Nothing.

284
00:13:35,660 --> 00:13:36,320
Be careful.

285
00:13:36,330 --> 00:13:37,130
You too.

286
00:13:37,950 --> 00:13:39,960
Are crutches necessary?

287
00:13:40,950 --> 00:13:42,110
I thought if I made it look worse,

288
00:13:42,110 --> 00:13:43,790
my mom would let me take the day off.

289
00:13:43,790 --> 00:13:45,130
But even that didn't work out.

290
00:13:45,130 --> 00:13:46,060
What should I do?

291
00:13:46,190 --> 00:13:47,250
I guess I'm going to

292
00:13:47,350 --> 00:13:48,590
school on crutches—

293
00:13:48,950 --> 00:13:50,280
strong will despite the injury!

294
