but if you like the dried fish,

588
00:26:35,620 --> 00:26:36,820
there's plenty more.

589
00:26:37,110 --> 00:26:37,710
Plenty.

590
00:26:39,610 --> 00:26:40,030
Oh right,

591
00:26:40,030 --> 00:26:41,490
I'm making fish porridge.

592
00:26:42,170 --> 00:26:42,900
Kids,

593
00:26:43,010 --> 00:26:44,820
we'll have pancakes today!

594
00:26:44,840 --> 00:26:46,790
-Okay.
-Grandpa, you don't need to fuss.

595
00:26:46,790 --> 00:26:48,410
We'll need to go back after we finish these problems,

596
00:26:48,410 --> 00:26:50,230
or we'll get scolded if we're too late.

597
00:26:50,230 --> 00:26:50,980
No, no,

598
00:26:51,010 --> 00:26:51,950
stay and eat

599
00:26:51,950 --> 00:26:52,800
before you go.

600
00:26:52,830 --> 00:26:54,030
Eat before you leave.

601
00:26:54,510 --> 00:26:55,150
Have some.

602
00:26:55,170 --> 00:26:56,170
It's really good.

603
00:26:58,310 --> 00:27:00,290
Babao. I'll teach you.

604
00:27:00,310 --> 00:27:01,830
One for you and one for me.

605
00:27:01,830 --> 00:27:02,830
Do your homework.

606
00:27:12,270 --> 00:27:14,130
Yours is more detailed than mine.

607
00:27:18,870 --> 00:27:20,550
You...

608
00:27:20,550 --> 00:27:22,070
Why do you keep bringing

609
00:27:22,160 --> 00:27:23,890
these things home all the time?

610
00:27:24,130 --> 00:27:25,410
Qiang Xiaowa's place.

611
00:27:25,440 --> 00:27:26,730
We often go there.

612
00:27:26,830 --> 00:27:27,910
His grandpa always

613
00:27:27,930 --> 00:27:29,790
gives us these delicious things.

614
00:27:30,840 --> 00:27:32,750
Don't just take their stuff.

615
00:27:33,150 --> 00:27:34,450
Next time, if they need anything,

616
00:27:34,450 --> 00:27:36,680
give them something from our place in return.

617
00:27:36,680 --> 00:27:38,080
What do we have to give?

618
00:27:38,610 --> 00:27:39,090
Dad,

619
00:27:39,260 --> 00:27:40,930
can we give them some medicinal patches

620
00:27:40,930 --> 00:27:42,930
for his grandpa's leg and back pain?

621
00:27:43,100 --> 00:27:43,870
Sure,

622
00:27:44,110 --> 00:27:45,480
some medicine as well.

623
00:27:45,510 --> 00:27:46,720
It's hard for them to get medicine over there.

624
00:27:46,720 --> 00:27:47,360
Dad.

625
00:27:47,710 --> 00:27:48,510
What about...

626
00:27:48,670 --> 00:27:49,230
Try this.

627
00:27:49,350 --> 00:27:50,020
What's this?

628
00:27:50,020 --> 00:27:50,710
Dried fish.

629
00:27:50,730 --> 00:27:51,990
It's sweet. Is it good?

630
00:27:52,100 --> 00:27:52,830
Yes.

631
00:27:53,280 --> 00:27:54,960
Dad, how's the information

632
00:27:54,990 --> 00:27:56,570
about the cochlear implant coming along?

633
00:27:56,570 --> 00:27:57,900
My comrades and I have sent out letters.

634
00:27:57,900 --> 00:27:59,830
We're just waiting for a response.

635
00:28:00,210 --> 00:28:00,840
Great.

636
00:28:02,110 --> 00:28:02,750
My comrade

637
00:28:02,750 --> 00:28:04,230
mentioned a girl

638
00:28:04,230 --> 00:28:05,550
with a similar condition

639
00:28:05,550 --> 00:28:06,670
to Zi,

640
00:28:07,230 --> 00:28:09,230
and her surgery was very successful.

641
00:28:09,230 --> 00:28:09,830
So,

642
00:28:09,830 --> 00:28:11,030
Zi's surgery

643
00:28:11,030 --> 00:28:12,190
should go smoothly too.

644
00:28:12,190 --> 00:28:13,300
That's amazing!

645
00:28:14,140 --> 00:28:15,540
-Great!
-This silly kid.

646
00:28:16,230 --> 00:28:17,110
Uncle Cheng.

647
00:28:17,310 --> 00:28:18,640
Where is this hospital?

648
00:28:18,690 --> 00:28:19,530
In Beijing.

649
00:28:19,790 --> 00:28:20,310
My comrade

650
00:28:20,310 --> 00:28:21,640
is reaching out to them.

651
00:28:22,640 --> 00:28:23,800
How much

652
00:28:23,940 --> 00:28:25,300
will the surgery cost?

653
00:28:28,010 --> 00:28:29,470
Dad, just tell us directly.

654
00:28:29,470 --> 00:28:31,800
It'll probably cost around 100,000 yuan.

655
00:28:32,720 --> 00:28:34,230
100,000?

656
00:28:34,230 --> 00:28:34,950
Yes,

657
00:28:35,150 --> 00:28:36,760
but given Zi's situation,

658
00:28:36,840 --> 00:28:38,900
we can apply for special financial aid

659
00:28:38,900 --> 00:28:40,850
from the Children's Foundation.

660
00:28:40,910 --> 00:28:41,590
If that's approved,

661
00:28:41,590 --> 00:28:43,310
we would only need to

662
00:28:43,540 --> 00:28:45,540
cover about 50,000 yuan ourselves.

663
00:28:47,270 --> 00:28:48,110
50,000...

664
00:28:53,040 --> 00:28:56,040
Honestly, I've never really resigned myself to fate.

665
00:28:56,810 --> 00:28:58,070
I always believed that

666
00:28:59,100 --> 00:29:00,560
as long as I didn't give up,

667
00:29:01,490 --> 00:29:03,220
I could push through anything.

668
00:29:05,100 --> 00:29:05,930
But tell me—

669
00:29:08,730 --> 00:29:09,930
does heaven

670
00:29:10,900 --> 00:29:12,630
have it out for me or something?

671
00:29:15,390 --> 00:29:16,720
No matter how hard I try,

672
00:29:19,310 --> 00:29:21,570
it seems like bad things keep happening.

673
00:29:23,150 --> 00:29:25,350
My grandma used to pray to Guanyin a lot.

674
00:29:26,300 --> 00:29:27,560
She'd chant prayers every day,

675
00:29:27,560 --> 00:29:29,020
asking heaven to bless us.

676
00:29:30,230 --> 00:29:31,700
So, when I was little,

677
00:29:31,730 --> 00:29:33,530
I thought she was so superstitious,

678
00:29:33,530 --> 00:29:36,260
always messing around with deities and spirits.

679
00:29:36,290 --> 00:29:37,230
I wanted her

680
00:29:37,230 --> 00:29:38,480
to give it up

681
00:29:38,920 --> 00:29:40,720
and believe in science instead.

682
00:29:43,660 --> 00:29:44,900
But later,

683
00:29:45,860 --> 00:29:46,900
when I grew up,

684
00:29:47,670 --> 00:29:48,730
I asked her one day,

685
00:29:49,190 --> 00:29:49,980
"Grandma,

686
00:29:50,390 --> 00:29:51,870
where is heaven anyway?

687
00:29:52,230 --> 00:29:54,230
What can it really protect us from?"

688
00:29:55,470 --> 00:29:56,730
You know what she said?

689
00:29:58,470 --> 00:30:00,260
She said, "Silly child,

690
00:30:00,290 --> 00:30:01,470
you've been going to school so long it's made you dumb.

691
00:30:01,470 --> 00:30:02,800
There is no heaven.

692
00:30:03,630 --> 00:30:05,960
I just give myself something to hold onto.

693
00:30:06,750 --> 00:30:08,070
I believe that

694
00:30:08,110 --> 00:30:09,700
as long as I think someone up there is protecting us,

695
00:30:09,700 --> 00:30:11,160
it keeps my spirit strong.

696
00:30:13,030 --> 00:30:13,790
You see,

697
00:30:13,790 --> 00:30:15,390
everyone faces tough times.

698
00:30:15,560 --> 00:30:17,070
Sometimes even drinking water

699
00:30:17,070 --> 00:30:18,400
feels like a struggle.

700
00:30:19,250 --> 00:30:19,930
But

701
00:30:20,170 --> 00:30:21,360
you can't let that struggle

702
00:30:21,360 --> 00:30:22,240
defeat you.

703
00:30:22,390 --> 00:30:24,120
Having something to believe in

704
00:30:25,270 --> 00:30:27,000
gives you the strength to think

705
00:30:28,170 --> 00:30:29,970
that this trouble can be solved,

706
00:30:30,050 --> 00:30:31,650
and things will get better."

707
00:30:34,320 --> 00:30:35,550
Wow, so many mistakes!

708
00:30:35,550 --> 00:30:37,460
-Who?
-Zhong Ruitao.

709
00:30:37,480 --> 00:30:37,970
Director.

710
00:30:37,970 --> 00:30:38,830
Are you eating?

711
00:30:38,860 --> 00:30:39,720
Director Xiao.

712
00:30:39,870 --> 00:30:41,130
Hello, Director Xiao.

713
00:30:41,600 --> 00:30:42,040
Director.

714
00:30:42,040 --> 00:30:43,020
This is mine.

715
00:30:43,250 --> 00:30:44,570
Ms. Han, thank you.

716
00:30:44,760 --> 00:30:45,800
Okay.

717
00:30:45,820 --> 00:30:46,320
Director Xiao,

718
00:30:46,320 --> 00:30:47,140
your current image

719
00:30:46,430 --> 00:30:47,340
[Donation Box]

720
00:30:47,190 --> 00:30:48,670
has reached new heights in my eyes.

721
00:30:48,670 --> 00:30:49,670
I'm not that great.

722
00:30:49,670 --> 00:30:50,780
It's more about having the right mindset.

723
00:30:50,780 --> 00:30:51,880
Absolutely! Absolutely!

724
00:30:51,880 --> 00:30:52,570
Director Xiao.

725
00:30:52,570 --> 00:30:53,330
Mine.

726
00:30:53,360 --> 00:30:54,330
Okay.

727
00:30:54,360 --> 00:30:55,000
Thank you.

728
00:30:55,590 --> 00:30:56,990
Zheng Weiwei, five yuan.

729
00:30:58,510 --> 00:30:59,310
Thank you.

730
00:31:00,520 --> 00:31:01,680
Wu Ziyi, 2.3 yuan.

731
00:31:06,260 --> 00:31:06,870
Thanks.

732
00:31:08,630 --> 00:31:09,870
Wang Fuqiang, 15.

733
00:31:10,860 --> 00:31:11,390
Cheng.

734
00:31:11,590 --> 00:31:13,070
This is all I've got left for the month.

735
00:31:13,070 --> 00:31:13,670
It's okay.

736
00:31:14,600 --> 00:31:15,200
Thank you.

737
00:31:16,310 --> 00:31:17,550
Zhong Ruitao, 20.

738
00:31:19,180 --> 00:31:19,780
Thank you.

739
00:31:21,780 --> 00:31:23,020
Li Jun, ten yuan.

740
00:31:23,360 --> 00:31:24,080
Five yuan.

741
00:31:24,110 --> 00:31:24,710
Thank you.

742
00:31:25,730 --> 00:31:26,970
Guo Xiao, five yuan.

743
00:31:32,460 --> 00:31:33,790
What are you looking at?

744
00:31:34,510 --> 00:31:36,110
Do you think it's too little?

745
00:31:36,600 --> 00:31:37,120
No.

746
00:31:38,310 --> 00:31:38,910
Thank you.

747
00:31:44,670 --> 00:31:44,990
Will the surgery

748
00:31:44,990 --> 00:31:46,520
make her able to hear again?

749
00:31:46,820 --> 00:31:47,350
Yes.

750
00:31:48,150 --> 00:31:48,880
That's good.

751
00:31:49,710 --> 00:31:50,830
This donation

752
00:31:51,390 --> 00:31:53,430
is not only for one person,

753
00:31:53,850 --> 00:31:55,080
not just for Yuan Shanqing,

754
00:31:55,080 --> 00:31:56,180
but for the cohesion

755
00:31:56,180 --> 00:31:58,420
of our entire group.

756
00:31:59,020 --> 00:31:59,910
Here,

757
00:32:00,390 --> 00:32:01,110
as the Director of Teaching,

758
00:32:01,110 --> 00:32:02,350
I, Xiao Fang,

759
00:32:02,350 --> 00:32:03,790
make a promise to everyone:

760
00:32:03,790 --> 00:32:04,390
As long as you are

761
00:32:04,390 --> 00:32:06,190
a part of Linqi No. 2 High School,

762
00:32:06,920 --> 00:32:09,030
no matter who faces difficulties,

763
00:32:09,510 --> 00:32:10,580
our school will

764
00:32:10,580 --> 00:32:12,110
always lend a helping hand,

765
00:32:12,280 --> 00:32:13,480
without hesitation.

766
00:32:14,050 --> 00:32:15,580
Can everyone commit to this?

767
00:32:15,580 --> 00:32:17,090
-Yes!
-Yes!

768
00:32:55,360 --> 00:32:56,860
There is true kindness in the world.

769
00:32:56,860 --> 00:32:58,590
There is true love in the world.

770
00:32:58,750 --> 00:33:00,350
Thousands of small families

771
00:33:00,350 --> 00:33:01,240
unite to form

772
00:33:01,240 --> 00:33:03,100
the big family of Linqi Oilfield.

773
00:33:03,890 --> 00:33:06,640
When one person faces hardship, help comes from all directions.

774
00:33:06,640 --> 00:33:08,080
This is the promise Linqi Oilfield makes

775
00:33:08,080 --> 00:33:10,030
to all its people.

776
00:33:10,760 --> 00:33:13,000
We call on everyone

777
00:33:13,130 --> 00:33:14,900
to offer your love

778
00:33:15,230 --> 00:33:17,280
and do what you can

779
00:33:17,570 --> 00:33:19,900
to support Yuan Shanqing.

780
00:33:27,850 --> 00:33:29,130
Dear teachers

781
00:33:28,230 --> 00:33:32,790
[Letter of thanks]

782
00:33:29,360 --> 00:33:30,280
and fellow students,

783
00:33:30,280 --> 00:33:31,280
Hello, everyone.

784
00:33:31,760 --> 00:33:34,020
I am Yuan Shanqing from Class 1, Grade 10.

785
00:33:34,790 --> 00:33:35,920
In the past few days,

786
00:33:36,040 --> 00:33:37,910
I've received donations and encouragement

787
00:33:37,910 --> 00:33:41,110
from the teachers, students, and people of the oilfield.

788
00:33:41,350 --> 00:33:43,680
I am incredibly touched by your kindness.

789
00:33:43,980 --> 00:33:45,210
Thank you for every penny

790
00:33:45,210 --> 00:33:46,720
you've donated

791
00:33:46,750 --> 00:33:48,150
and every word of comfort

792
00:33:48,270 --> 00:33:50,600
you've shared for my sister, Yuan Shanzi.

793
00:33:51,380 --> 00:33:52,220
Both Shanzi and I

794
00:33:52,220 --> 00:33:53,690
will always remember

795
00:33:54,200 --> 00:33:55,280
your kindness

796
00:33:55,300 --> 00:33:57,410
and the love you've shown us.

797
00:33:58,760 --> 00:34:00,490
I promise to work twice as hard,

798
00:34:00,670 --> 00:34:02,000
and one day,

799
00:34:02,230 --> 00:34:03,620
I will repay Linqi Oilfield

800
00:34:03,620 --> 00:34:04,480
and our school.

801
00:34:05,570 --> 00:34:07,820
Once again, I express my deepest gratitude

802
00:34:07,820 --> 00:34:09,440
to each and every one of you.

803
00:34:09,900 --> 00:34:11,500
Thank you for your kindness,

804
00:34:12,730 --> 00:34:14,330
and I wish you all good health

805
00:34:14,480 --> 00:34:15,540
and happiness.

806
00:34:16,750 --> 00:34:17,699
Yuan Shanqing.

807
00:34:19,800 --> 00:34:21,800
Now, I have an announcement to make.

808
00:34:22,380 --> 00:34:23,750
For this poetry reading contest,

809
00:34:23,750 --> 00:34:24,810
one student's poem

810
00:34:25,020 --> 00:34:26,710
stood out to me

811
00:34:26,730 --> 00:34:28,100
as exceptionally well-written.

812
00:34:28,100 --> 00:34:29,139
So I've decided

813
00:34:29,230 --> 00:34:30,880
to use this student's poem

814
00:34:30,909 --> 00:34:32,080
as our class's entry,

815
00:34:32,080 --> 00:34:34,770
and this student will lead the recitation.

816
00:34:37,380 --> 00:34:39,040
Let's quiet down for a moment.

817
00:34:39,150 --> 00:34:40,510
I'm sure you're all curious

818
00:34:40,510 --> 00:34:41,750
about who it is, right?

819
00:34:41,750 --> 00:34:42,670
Yes.

820
00:34:45,489 --> 00:34:46,600
Yuan Shanqing.

821
00:34:50,239 --> 00:34:51,300
Congratulations.

