00:35:49,520 --> 00:35:51,290
This color is so beautiful.

847
00:35:51,920 --> 00:35:52,720
This is good.

848
00:35:52,780 --> 00:35:54,300
Teacher, easy, easy.

849
00:35:54,690 --> 00:35:55,370
Here.

